Nope.  Wrong wrong wrong.<br>
<br>
There's zero recast on the bracer.<br>
You can chain cast it.<br>
The mob is stunned for the first 3 seconds of your 2nd bracer use.<br>
The mob is stunned for the first 3 seconds of your 3rd bracer use.<br>
Etc.<br>
You don't wait for the stun to wear off before beginning to bracer again.<br>
You chain bracer without stopping. <p>=============================
