I've timed it multiple times.  It's a 6 and 3 seconds respectively.<br>
<br>
It does work to slow mobs.  I know this for a fact because I've used it for just such a purpose on my paladin.  The mob gets 1 attack against you before your bracer finishes casting.  You can quite easily channel a spell through 1 attack.  If you get bashed or interupted for some reason, that's when you cast your stun spell for 30 mana, then resume chain bracering.  It works wonderfully.<br>
