<br>
As a monk i value Hp gear and sta very high, and its the main thing i look for in new items. Using my normal setup of equip im about 20hp shy of 2300hp with no buffs whatsoever while maintaining around 1087ac or 1099 with my epic on. Im pretty sure you would benefit from swapping some wis gear with HP/AC gear, stats are overrated in most cases. And most xp groups have a chanter for a wis buff and remember your wis is just your mana pool, and since most paladin spells you use in a group (mainly stuns) is very low mana i doubt a sligtly smaller mana pool would be too much of a problem, with C2 i doubt you'd have any problems even if your wis was 20 points lower.<br>
<br>
Just my opinion, use it or disregard it at your whim.<br>
<br>
